<refsect1 id="rssfeeda">
<title>Example</title>
<itemizedlist mark="bullet">
<listitem>The application allow users to retreive a RSS2 documents and render as Weblog.</listitem>
<listitem>The RSS2 file will be transformed to a Updategram and stored in a local table.</listitem>
<listitem>Also it demonstrates the usage of VSPX calendar used for navigation.</listitem>
<listitem>The application contains a simple RSS2 generator, used to present a BLOG data on local server.</listitem>
<listitem>The data on local server can be entered using the <ulink url="../blog/blog.vsp">BLOG</ulink> application</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</refsect1>

</refentry>
